name.text:
Dose # 1 PCV 13 at 24 mo-5 days.  Valid but child needs another. 
Evaluation_Test_Type: All Valid: Forecast Test
General_Description: This test case describes when a child is administered the first dose of the Pneumococcal 13 vaccine at 24 months - 5 days, that the dose is considered to be valid, but a second dose is still needed.
